  body class="#{page_classes}"
    main.site-wrap
      nav.site-nav
        ul.site-nav--list
          li.site-nav--element
            a.site-nav--link href="#"
              | Cases
          li.site-nav--element.site-nav--active
            a.site-nav--link href="#"
              | Mission
          li.site-nav--element
            a.site-nav--link href="#"
              | Lab
          li.site-nav--element
            a.site-nav--link href="#"
              | Collab   
      section#masthead.site-block.site-block--small-height.site-block--max-width
        .container-fluid
          .row
            .col-6
              .masthead-logo
                == link_to 'Made by Porter', '/'
            .col-6
              a.pull-right.comp-btn.comp-btn-red href="#" Work With Me
      section#hero.site-block.site-block--small-height.site-block--max-width
        .container-fluid
          .row
            .col-12
              h1
                | Workin' &amp; Chillin'
              p.paragraph-large
                | Chris Porter is an independent creative, building for passion projects &amp; startups.
      section#cases.site-block.site-block--full-width
        .site-block.site-block--max-width.site-block--small-height
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-12
                h2
                  | Case Studies
        #caseStudies.case-studies
          #caseAdvancerLeft.case-studies--advancer.case-studies--advancer-left
            | Left
          #caseAdvancerRight.case-studies--advancer.case-studies--advancer-right
            | Right
          div#caseStudiesWrap.case-studies--wrap
            ul#caseStudiesContents.case-studies--contents
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
              li.case-studies--block
      section#mission.site-block.site-block--full-width.style-mission
        .site-block.site-block--max-width.site-block--small-height
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-12
                h2
                  | Mission
            .row
              .col-md-6
                p
                  | <span class="sub-title">Work Smarter, Not Harder.</span>
                p
                  | This was my dad's favorite quote when I was younger. He always emphasized the importance of having an effective yet efficient workflow.

                p
                  | Today, that is the blood that runs through my veins. My passion is to help brands and people improve their businesses and lives by providing better design, visuals and multimedia.

                h3
                  | Here's my deep dives:
                ul.comp-list
                  li
                    | Native App Design
                  li
                    | Web App Design
                  li
                    | Marketing Website Design
                  li
                    | HTML &amp; CSS Development

                h3
                  | What I do from time to time:
                ul.comp-list
                  li
                    | Identity Branding
                  li
                    | Print Design
                  li
                    | Music Production
                  li
                    | Photography

      section#lab.site-block.site-block--full-width.style-lab
        .site-block.site-block--max-width.site-block--small-height
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-12
                h2
                  | Lab
            .row
              .col-md-6
                p
                  | <span class="sub-title">Want to know what I'm working on?</span>
                p
                  | Here's my latest design work from <a href="http://www.dribbble.com/madebyporter">Dribbble</a>.
            .row
              .col-md-12
                div.js-grid.my-shuffle
      section#lab.site-block.site-block--full-width.style-collab
        .site-block.site-block--max-width.site-block--small-height
          .container-fluid
            .row
              .col-12
                h2
                  | Collab
            .row
              .col-md-6
                p
                  | <span class="sub-title">Want to work together on something cool?</span>
                p
                  | I'm booked for the rest of the year, however, I am open to future projects starting as early as February 2018. Get in touch.
                p
                  a.comp-btn.comp-btn-red href="#" Work With Me
                
    
